"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-olympics-news-from-shilese-jones-to-sophia-smith-24-women-to-watch-ahead-of-the-2024-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The Paris Olympics are 100 days away and there are many female athletes to keep an eye on.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 90, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simone Bilesis expected to make her return to the Olympic stage,Sha'Carri Richardsonlooks to make her Olympic debut in the sprints for the U.S. track and field team andKatie Ledeckyhopes to further cement her status as history's greatest female distance swimmer.\", \"from\": 92, \"to\": 354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These three highlight a talented cast of women expected to represent the U.S. in Paris.\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 437, \"end\": 442, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5254184417188327e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the Games will features thousands of female athletes contending for medals and Olympic history, we are calling out just a handful of key names to know (24, to be exact) as the countdown to the 2024 Paris Olympics heats up.\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Qualification for many major sports will happen later this summer, but in the meantime here's a look at some of the biggest names we expect to see in action in Paris.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5254184417188327e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Known as the GOAT,Simone Bilesis widely considered the greatest female gymnast of all time.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2016 Olympic all-around champion has won seven Olympic medals, including four gold, and holds the record for most medals in world championships history with 30.\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1098, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After withdrawing from most of her events at the Tokyo Olympics in 2021, Biles is expected to make her highly anticipated return to the Olympic stage in Paris.\", \"from\": 1099, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1252, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5254184417188327e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shilese Jonesis one of the key contenders for the U.S. Olympic team in Paris.\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1331, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5254184417188327e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is the 2023 world all-around bronze medalist and is particularly impressive on the uneven bars.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her father passed away in December of 2021 and Jones has dedicated this Olympic journey to him.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"LIVERPOOL, ENGLAND - NOVEMBER 03: Rebeca Andrade of Brazil reacts after their routine on the Uneven Bars during Women's All-Around Final on day six of the 2022 Gymnastics World Championships at M&S Bank Arena on November 03, 2022 in Liverpool, England.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1535, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999867459338, \"rank\": 1.32437656818