_revoltosa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_revoltosa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The nickname comes from her grandmother, who died in 2019 after violence broke out close to her home in Mexico.\", \"from\": 8436, \"to\": 8547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8540, \"end\": 8546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6084879151504367, \"rank\": 0.6391160469160156, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lozano says she aims to honor her grandmother by making trouble for her opponents in the ring.\", \"from\": 8548, \"to\": 8642, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She reached the semifinals at two international tournaments in 2023 and qualified for Paris by reaching the final bout at the 2023 Pan American Games.\", \"from\": 8643, \"to\": 8793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8729, \"end\": 8734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5254184417188327e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 8774, \"end\": 8792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"score\": 0.9986307632862458, \"rank\": 0.0013711140211921647, \"text\": \"Pan American Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_American_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is expected to become the first Olympian from Laredo, Texas.\", \"from\": 8794, \"to\": 8858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8830, \"end\": 8838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999736247, \"rank\": 2.6779689328311968e-11, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbp